casebody.data:
Enoch Rutzler, Appellant, v. William Belden, Respondent. Decided June 8, 1886. Appeal from judgment entered upon verdict directed by court. Flanagan & Hamlin, for appellant. Marsh, Wilson & Marsh, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, • Oh. J. and Truax, J.

Opinion

Per Curiam.

Judgment set aside ; new trial ordered ; costs of appeal to abide event.
